overview:
Tab-Midcities, a unit of Tab Group is an advisory board and business consulting service provider for giving best solution to your business of all problem in any circumstances. Its expert advisory board is experienced and highly qualified in business solution field. The Alternative Board® (TAB) is an organization that provides peer advisory boards and executive coaching services for business owners, CEOs and presidents worldwide. Thousands of business owners of small- and medium-sized companies are members of TAB boards. There are over 140 TAB franchises operating in five countries, including the US, Canada, the United Kingdom and New Zealand Major offered services are:- • small business mentor • small business networking • business success stories • small business resources small business tips

So do not be late and get solution of your business problem. For more information please visit www.tab-midcities.com Address- Ray Champney PO Box 1072 Bedford, TX 76095-1072 Phone: 817-318-1233 Fax: 817-318-1543
